🧩 Usage Guide — RDT Kernel
Recursive Diffusion-Type Kernel (RDT)

Author: Steven Reid (RRG314)
License: MIT

📘 Introduction

The RDT Kernel (rdt_kernel) provides a nonlinear, entropy-regulated diffusion operator for evolving scalar fields in PyTorch.

It is designed to model field dynamics of the form:

∂
𝐿
